# Learning to be Safe

This repository contains code (in-development) for safety-constrained
[Soft Actor-Critic](https://github.com/rail-berkeley/softlearning), using
the [TF-Agents](https://github.com/tensorflow/agents) library.

## Setup

First, install all dependencies by

pip install -r safemrl/requirements.txt


## Usage

```
# Running Safe SAC example on Drunk Spider navigation environment
python -m safemrl.train --gin_file=sac_agent_drunk.gin
```

```
# Running Safe SAC example on Minitaur environment
python -m safemrl.train --gin_file=sac_minitaur.gin
```
